<h3>PNC Shortcodes</h3>
<h4>&#091;pnc_link_button&#093;</h4>
<p><strong>Parameters:</strong> class=""(optional), href="", target=""(optional), text=""</p>
<p><strong>class:</strong> What class to give the link button, default: button-p</p>
<p><strong>href:</strong> Location to send user, example: /test would go to the test page</p>
<p><strong>target:</strong> Frame to open the link in, default: _self, NOTE: use _blank to open in a new window</p>
<p><strong>text:</strong> This is the text of the link button</p>
<h5>Example Usage</h5>
<pre>
&#091;pnc_link_button class="button-p" href="/" target="_blank" text="Example Button" &#093;
</pre>
<h5>Rendering</h5>
[pnc_link_button class="button-p" href="/" target="_blank" text="Example Button"];

<h4>&#091;pnc_alert&#093;</h4>
<p><strong>Parameters:</strong> class="", text=""</p>
<p><strong>class:</strong> What class to give the alert, default: default</p>
<p><strong>class choices:</strong> success, success-radius, success-round, warning, warning-radius, warning-round, danger, danger-radius, danger-round, default, default-radius, default-round, info, info-radius, info-round, secondary, secondary-radius, secondary-round</p>
<p><strong>text:</strong> This is the text of the alert</p>
<h5>Example Usage</h5>
<pre>
&#091;pnc_alert class="secondary-radius" text="Example Alert Secondary Radius" &#093;
</pre>
<h5>Rendering</h5>
[pnc_alert class="secondary-radius" text="Example Alert Secondary Radius"]

